.TH "CITADEL" "1" "Jan 2026" "AceTeam" "Citadel CLI Manual"

.SH NAME
citadel - Citadel is the agent for the AceTeam Sovereign Compute Fabric


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcitadel [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
A self-contained agent and CLI for connecting your hardware
to the AceTeam control plane, making your resources available to your private workflows.

.PP
When run without a subcommand, Citadel starts interactive mode with slash commands.
Use 'citadel help' to see all available commands.


.SH OPTIONS
\fB--auth-service\fP="https://aceteam.ai"
	The URL of the authentication service

.PP
\fB--config\fP=""
	config file (default is $HOME/.citadel-cli.yaml)

.PP
\fB--daemon\fP[=false]
	Run in background daemon mode (no TUI)

.PP
\fB--debug\fP[=false]
	Enable debug output

.PP
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for citadel

.PP
\fB--nexus\fP="https://nexus.aceteam.ai"
	The URL of the AceTeam Nexus server


